Scenario: Verify complete user response
  Given url baseUrl
  And path 'users', 1
  When method get
  Then status 200
  And assert responseTime < 2000
  And match responseHeaders['Content-Type'][0] contains 'application/json'
  And match response ==
  {
    id: '#number',
    name: '#string',
    role: '#string',
    active: '#boolean'
  }
-----Match each 
When method get
Then status 200
And match each response.data ==
"""
{
  "id": "#string",
  "employee_name": "#string",
  "employee_salary": "#string",
  "employee_age": "#string",
  "profile_image": "##string"
}
"""
##string = optional field

Meaning:

Field present ho → string honi chahiye

Field missing ho → bhi test PASS karega

----
One-line rule (YAAD RAKHO)

Object → match response
Array → match each response
